# The store catalog is a public, machine-readable API consumed by the
# ClawLego app. Allow cross-origin reads for the whole /store/ namespace.
# 注意：Workers 静态资源对重叠的 _headers 规则是「追加」而非「覆盖」，
# 所以这里只保留一条 /store/* 规则。若再加一条 /store/index.json，
# 会让命中两条规则的路径出现 `Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *, *`
# 这种非法重复值，浏览器跨域 fetch 会被拒。
/store/*
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=300
